asset.hookText:
Lyzabeth's Beauty Shake


1 scoop of your favorite protein powder
1/2 - 1 cup vanilla or chocolate almond milk
1 tbls aloe vera juice
1 tbls silica
1 tbls gogi juice
1/4 tsp acidophilus
1 tsp bee pollen
1 tsp maca root powder
1 tbls EFA

In a blender, add:
1 scoop chocolate Vega Whole Health Optimizer  
1 cup vanilla or chocolate almond milk
All other ingredients and blend. 

Pour and enjoy!
